scenes.description: The audience chants "Encore!" enthusiastically while the stage remains dark.
Momosuzu Nene returns to the stage, showcasing her new jacket and announcing the final song.
Momosuzu Nene performs the song 'ebb and flow'.
Momosuzu Nene thanks the audience and shows off her jacket once more as the live stream nears its end.
